glosses.gloss: Apt. is the fifth album by Chilean singer Nicole.
APT is a 2006 South Korean horror film, directed, produced, and written by Ahn Byeong-ki and starring Ko So-young.
Apt is a commune in the Vaucluse department in the Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur region in southeastern France.
Advanced Package Tool, or APT, is a free software user interface that works with core libraries to handle the installation and removal of software on Debian, Ubuntu and other Linux distributions.
Debian's high-level package management system, also used by other Linux-based operating systems
어드밴스트 패키징 툴은 코어 라이브러리와 함께 동작하는 자유 사용자 인터페이스로, 데비안 GNU/리눅스 배포판 계열 배포판에서 소프트웨어를 설치하고 제거하는 일을 한다.
